| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0178 — Recovery Inhibition (royal)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ae8d14ce-1bdc-5b9b-8ea3-16c1c47e1a31"
